# CiviCRM Add Ons #

Custom scripts for CiviCRM implementation.

Includes:

1. TIGGER: When [custom data field: member number] is imported. ACTION: Send email from [template: login instructions] to each member.

2. TRIGGER: When new Member Type is [student]. ACTION: Pop up/lightbox window to agree to special terms & conditions. Record that agreement in [custom data field: student terms].

3. TRIGGER: When new Member Type is [developing nation] AND member form is submitted. ACTION: Check billing country to see if it is on the list of developing nations.

4. Button to email customer profile to 3rd-party. Based on "Email Contact" functionality. Sends customer name, customer number, and mailing address profile to members of Group "Publisher".

